trans-unit.source: Represents an error that occurred during composition.
trans-unit.target: Representa un error que se ha producido durante la composición.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> or <see langword="null" /> to set the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> property to an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Un mensaje que describe el objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />, o <see langword="null" /> para establecer la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> en una cadena vacía ("").

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> class with the specified error message.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> con el mensaje de error especificado.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> or <see langword="null" /> to set the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> property to an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Un mensaje que describe el objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />, o <see langword="null" /> para establecer la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> en una cadena vacía ("").

trans-unit.source: The composition element that is the cause of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> or <see langword="null" /> to set the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Element" /> property to <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Elemento de composición que es la causa de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />, o <see langword="null" /> para establecer la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Element" /> en <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> class with the specified error message and the composition element that is the cause of the composition error.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> con el mensaje de error especificado y el elemento de composición que causa el error de composición.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> or <see langword="null" /> to set the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> property to an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Un mensaje que describe el objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />, o <see langword="null" /> para establecer la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> en una cadena vacía ("").

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Exception" /> that is the underlying cause of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> or <see langword="null" /> to set the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Exception" /> property to <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Exception" /> que es la causa subyacente de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />, o <see langword="null" /> para establecer la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Exception" /> en <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> class with the specified error message and the exception that is the cause of the composition error.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una instancia nueva de la clase <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> con el mensaje de error especificado y una referencia a la excepción interna que causa el error de composición.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> or <see langword="null" /> to set the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> property to an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Un mensaje que describe el objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />, o <see langword="null" /> para establecer la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> en una cadena vacía ("").

trans-unit.source: The composition element that is the cause of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> or <see langword="null" /> to set the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Element" /> property to <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Elemento de composición que es la causa de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />, o <see langword="null" /> para establecer la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Element" /> en <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Exception" /> that is the underlying cause of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> or <see langword="null" /> to set the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Exception" /> property to <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Exception" /> que es la causa subyacente de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />, o <see langword="null" /> para establecer la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Exception" /> en <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> class with the specified error message, and the composition element and exception that are the cause of the composition error.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" /> con el mensaje de error especificado y el elemento de composición y la excepción que son la causa del error de composición.

trans-unit.source: Gets a description of the composition error.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene una descripción del error de composición.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />.
trans-unit.target: Un mensaje que describe el error <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the composition element that is the cause of the error.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el elemento de composición que es la causa del error.

trans-unit.source: The composition element that is the cause of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />.
trans-unit.target: Elemento de composición que es la causa de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the exception that is the underlying cause of the composition error.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la excepción que es la causa subyacente del error de composición.

trans-unit.source: The exception that is the underlying cause of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />.
trans-unit.target: Excepción que es la causa subyacente de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns a string representation of the composition error.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve una representación de cadena del error de composición.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" /> property.
trans-unit.target: Una cadena que contiene la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CompositionError.Description" />.
